{
  "stem": "3474.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Rehmsdorf was already a camp, because it was almost the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People were being dragged there from all the camps there together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what people were already tired, tired of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were skinny, no food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "People were just dying like flies over there, and work, and work, and work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They used to chase us [INAUDIBLE] and hit us all the time-- work faster and work faster.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's like, just like there was not too much to do, anyway.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they were just chasing, do, and do, and do, and do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We used to, we used to drag the machine from one place to another and fixing here, move it from one place to the other.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was just terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And people were dying over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as I said before, and they used to go around with a push cart like banan-- like if you've ever seen New York when they push the push cart of the bananas.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They used to pick up the bodies from the, from the, from the barracks, put them on that push cart, bring them over to like a mountain over there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They used to put them on top each other, just throw them on there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Nothing, nobody but-- it was just like when you go over here to a dirt mountain when in fact, you just watch.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's like it doesn't bother you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was terrible there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "People were dying like crazy there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there was no water there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there was supposed to be a washroom over there but no water.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And in there, they used to get people that was almost dead.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There was one person that used to come with an SS all the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
